"No physical volumes were selected. The creation of a new ZFS pool has been "
"aborted."
msgstr ""
"Ni ddewiswyd unrhyw gyfrolau corfforol. Mae creu y pwll ZFS newydd wedi ei "
"derfynu."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#. :sl4:
#: ../partman-zfs.templates:28001
